title: Above & Beyond 55+ Living In a 2 BR Apt at The Legends of Woodbury!
map_address: 570 Settlers Ridge Parkway near Hudson Rd
posting_body: ['At the Legends of Woodbury, we are giving 55+ living a whole new meaning.', 'We are proud to say that we have strategically placed this brand new community conveniently near the neighborhoods top-of-the-line shopping spots and even next to some fantastic restaurants.', 'If the grandkids are in town, we even have several parks in the area!', 'The Legends of Woodbury offers one, two and three bedroom spacious apartment homes.', 'These options come with a variety of floor plans that you will love!', 'As far as amenities go, you can’t beat the ones that we provide.', 'We have a fitness center, craft/card room, a landscaped outdoor patio, a community room, a theater room, heated underground parking garage and even a washer and dryer included in every home!', 'We want our residents to love their home, which is why we have a professional on-site management team and 24-hour emergency maintenance service.', 'Have a dog?', 'Great!', 'The Legends of Woodbury is a pet-friendly community that even has an outdoor play area for your dog.', 'Let yourself live the 55+ living dream and call today to schedule your tour!', 'NOTE: Office Hours - By Appointment Only.', 'Community Amenities Include:', '- Professional On-Site Management Team', '- State-Of-The-Art Fitness Center', '- Full-Size Washer & Dryer', 'In EVERY Home!', '- 24-Hour Emergency Maintenance Service', '- Open & Spacious Floor Plans', '- Kitchen Breakfast Bar or Island', 'We are a pet-friendly community.', 'Dogs & cats welcome!', '*Comfortable living does not have to be high dollar.', 'The Legends of Woodbury is a community for active seniors that participates in an affordable housing program.', 'Household income & student status limitations apply: 1 Occupant: $49,320 | 2', 'Occupants: $56,340 | 3', 'Occupants: $63,360 | 4 Occupants: $70,380 | 5 Occupants: $76,020 | 6', 'Occupants: $81,660.', 'At least one household member must be at least 55 years of age.', 'To maintain the integrity of the community; credit, rental & public record background checks are conducted on all applicants.', 'Office Hours:', 'Monday-Friday:9:00AM-5:00PM', 'Call today to schedule your tour:', 'show contact info', 'Legends of Woodbury', '570 Settlers Ridge Parkway', 'Woodbury, MN, 55129', '<URL>', '*Some Restrictions May Apply.', 'IKJMQ2g0d']
